title: Episode 33: Trader Joe's 12th Annual Customer Choice Awards Winners
itunes:title: Trader Joe's 12th Annual Customer Choice Awards Winners
description:
The votes have been cast, the ballots have been tallied, and the winners have been verified! Inside this episode of Inside Trader Joe’s we reveal the results of the 12th Annual Customer Choice Awards. From Favorite Cheese to Best Beverage and Favorite Trader Joe’s Product Overall, this awards show has everything other awards shows have, and has been proven to be 242% more delicious.
